# .totalschemaignore — files and directories excluded from TotalSchema change-file discovery.
# Syntax mirrors .gitignore:
#   - Lines starting with # are comments.
#   - Patterns ending with / are directory patterns (the directory and its contents are skipped).
#   - Patterns containing / are matched against the full relative path from the changes root.
#   - Patterns without / are matched against the file or directory name anywhere in the tree.

# Ignore the Python helper-library directory used by the python3 connector sample.
# The library lives inside the changes tree so TotalSchema can resolve it relative to the
# workspace, but it must not be treated as a set of change files.

*.log